############################Scheduler Manager Sequence diagrams - Full workflow############################

### **Complete Scheduler Cycle: Task Creation, Execution, Update, and Removal**

```plaintext
User          Scheduler         TaskManager        UIDManager         PQ  
  |                |                  |                  |             |           
  | Create Task    |                  |                  |             |              
  |---------------->|                  |                  |             |              
  |                | Create Task      |                  |             |              
  |                |------------------>|                  |             |              
  |                | Generate UID     |                  |             |           
  |                |------------------>| Generate UID     |             |               
  |                |                   |----------------->|             |
  |                |                   |Get Counter,PID,TS|             |               
  |                |                   | Return UID       |             |               
  |                |  UID Generated    |<-----------------|             | 
  |                |<------------------|                  |             |
  |                | Set Task Params  |                  |             |
  |                |----------------->|                  |             |
  |                | Set Execution Time|                  |             |
  |                |<------------------|                  |             |
  |                | Add Task to PQ    |                  |             |       
  |                |----------------->| Insert to PQ     |             |      
  |                |                   |----------------->| Insert Task |
  |                |  Task Inserted    |                  |             |
  |                |<------------------|                  |             |
  | Task Created   |                   |                  |             |
  |<----------------|                  |                  |             |
  | Execute Task   |                  |                  |             |
  |---------------->|                  |                  |             |
  |                | Get Next Task    |                  |             |
  |                |----------------->|                  |             |
  |                | Retrieve Task    |                  |             |
  |                |----------------->| Retrieve Task    |             |
  |                |                   |----------------->|             |
  |                |                   | Task Retrieved   |             |
  |                |<------------------|                  |             |
  |                | Execute Task      |                  |             |
  |                |----------------->| Execute OpFunc   |             |
  |                | Run Task Operation|                  |             |
  |                |----------------->| OpFunc()         |             |
  |                | Operation Complete|                  |             |
  |                |<-----------------|                  |             |
  |                | Update Task Time  |                  |             |
  |                |----------------->| Update Time      |             |
  |                |                   | New Exec Time    |             |
  |                |                   |----------------->|             |
  |                | Reinsert Task     |                  |             |
  |                |----------------->| Insert Task      |             |
  |                |                   |----------------->| Insert Task |
  |                |                   | Task Reinserted  |             |
  |                |<------------------|                  |             |
  | Task Executed  |                   |                  |             |
  |<----------------|                  |                  |             |
  | Erase Task     |                  |                  |             |
  |---------------->|                  |                  |             |
  |                | Find Task        |                  |             |
  |                |----------------->|                  |              |
  |                | Match Task       |                  |             |
  |                |----------------->| Search Task      |             |
  |                |                   |----------------->|             |
  |                |                   | Match Found      |             |
  |                |                   |<-----------------|             |
  |                | Remove Task      |                  |             |
  |                |----------------->| Remove Task      |             |
  |                |                   |----------------->|             |
  |                |                   | Task Removed     |             |
  |                |<------------------|                  |             |
  | Task Removed   |                   |                  |             |
  |<----------------|                  |                  |             |
  |                |                  |                  |             |
  | Insert Task    |                  |                  |             |
  |---------------->|                  |                  |             |
  |                | Insert Task to PQ |                  |             |
  |                |----------------->|                  |             |
  |                | Task Inserted    |                  |             |
  |                |<-----------------|                  |             |
  | Get Task       |                  |                  |             |
  |---------------->|                  |                  |             |
  |                | Retrieve Task    |                  |             |
  |                |----------------->|                  |             |
  |                | Task Retrieved   |                  |             |
  |                |<-----------------|                  |             |
  | Task Executed  |                  |                  |             |
  |<----------------|                 |                  |             |
  | Check Size     |                  |                  |             |
  |---------------->|                  |                  |             |
  |                | Size of PQ       |                  |             |
  |                |----------------->|                  |             |
  |                | Return Size      |                  |             |
  |                |<-----------------|                  |             |



### Summary of All Key Operations:
- **Task Creation** involves generating a UID and inserting it into the priority queue.
- **Task Execution** involves retrieving the task, executing it, and reinserting it if it's recurring.
- **Task Removal** involves finding the task in PQ and removing it.
- **UID Generation** involves the use of static counters, `getpid()`, and timestamps.
- **Priority Queue Operations** include insertion, retrieval, and size management.

This is a detailed breakdown of the entire scheduler workflow, combining task creation, execution, priority queue management, and UID generation. Let me know if any further refinements are needed!


############################Scheduler API############################

### `SchedCreate`

```plaintext
User          Scheduler          Priority Queue
  |                 |                    |
  | Create Scheduler|                    |
  |---------------->|                    |
  |                 | Create Priority Queue|
  |                 |------------------->|
  |                 | Priority Queue Created|
  |                 |<-------------------|
  | Scheduler Created|                    |
  |<----------------|                    |
```

---

### `SchedDestroy`

```plaintext
User          Scheduler          Priority Queue
  |                 |                    |
  | Destroy Scheduler|                    |
  |---------------->|                    |
  |                 | Clear Priority Queue|
  |                 |------------------->|
  |                 | Priority Queue Cleared|
  |                 |<-------------------|
  |                 | Free Memory        |
  |                 |------------------->|
  | Scheduler Destroyed|                 |
  |<----------------|                    |
```

---

### `AddTask`

```plaintext
User          Scheduler          Priority Queue      Task
  |                 |                    |              |
  | Add Task        |                    |              |
  |---------------->|                    |              |
  |                 | Create Task Object|              |
  |                 |------------------>|              |
  |                 |                    | Create UID   |
  |                 |                    |<-------------|
  |                 | Enqueue Task       |              |
  |                 |------------------->|              |
  |                 |                    | Task Enqueued|
  |                 |                    |<-------------|
  | Task Added      |                    |              |
  |<----------------|                    |              |
```

---

### `RemoveTask`

```plaintext
User          Scheduler          Priority Queue      Task
  |                 |                    |              |
  | Remove Task      |                    |              |
  |---------------->|                    |              |
  |                 | Check Current Task |              |
  |                 |------------------->|              |
  |                 |                    | Match UID    |
  |                 |                    |--------------|
  |                 |                    | Match Found  |
  |                 |                    |<-------------|
  |                 |                    | Remove Task  |
  |                 |                    |--------------|
  | Task Removed     |                    |              |
  |<----------------|                    |              |
```

---

### `SchedRun`

```plaintext
User          Scheduler          Priority Queue      Task
  |                 |                    |              |
  | Run Scheduler    |                    |              |
  |---------------->|                    |              |
  |                 | Dequeue Task       |              |
  |                 |------------------->|              |
  |                 |                    | Task Dequeued|
  |                 |                    |<-------------|
  |                 | Execute Task       |              |
  |                 |------------------->|              |
  |                 | Reschedule or Destroy Task        |
  |                 |<------------------|              |
  | Task Executed    |                    |              |
  |<----------------|                    |              |
```

---

### `SchedStop`

```plaintext
User          Scheduler
  |                 |
  | Stop Scheduler   |
  |---------------->|
  |                 | Update State to STOPPED
  |                 |-------------------------|
  | Scheduler Stopped|
  |<----------------|
```

---

### `SchedClear`

```plaintext
User          Scheduler          Priority Queue      Task
  |                 |                    |              |
  | Clear Scheduler  |                    |              |
  |---------------->|                    |              |
  |                 | Dequeue All Tasks  |              |
  |                 |------------------->|              |
  |                 |                    | Task Dequeued|
  |                 |                    |<-------------|
  |                 | Destroy Task       |              |
  |                 |------------------->|              |
  | Scheduler Cleared|                    |              |
  |<----------------|                    |              |
```

---

