### `UIDCreate`

```plaintext
User          UIDManager          TimeLibrary          OS
  |                 |                   |                |
  | Request UID      |                   |                |
  |---------------->|                   |                |
  |                 | Generate Counter   |                |
  |                 |------------------->|                |
  |                 |                    | Get PID        |
  |                 |--------------------|--------------->|
  |                 | Counter Generated  | PID Retrieved  |
  |                 |<------------------|<---------------|
  |                 | Generate Timestamp |                |
  |                 |------------------->Time()           |
  |                 | Timestamp Retrieved|                |
  |                 |<-------------------|                |
  | UID Generated    |                   |                |
  |<----------------|                   |                |
```

